c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1740597548/image_1740597548.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1740597548/image_1740597548.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1740597548/image_1740597548.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">hadynyah/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Aya Gold &amp; Silver</em> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AYASF\" title=\"Aya Gold &amp; Silver Inc.\">OTCQX:AYASF</a>) has been under scrutiny ever since early September 2024, when it <a href=\"https://ayagoldsilver.com/press-release/aya-gold-silver-updates-on-expansion-of-zgounder/\" rel=\"nofollow\">announced</a> a two-month delay in the hot commissioning and ramp-up of the expanded Zgounder plant in Morocco</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1740597548/image_1740597548.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743846-aya-gold-and-silver-ayasf-risky-but-worth-the-challenges", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 16:16:17"}, {"id": "4743865", "title": "Global Sugar Surplus Depends On India", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1053940858/image_1053940858.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"pile of sugar cubes with blue background and red background\" data-id=\"1053940858\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1039px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1053940858/image_1053940858.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1053940858/image_1053940858.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1053940858/image_1053940858.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1053940858/image_1053940858.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1053940858/image_1053940858.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1053940858/image_1053940858.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1053940858/image_1053940858.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1053940858/image_1053940858.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Tara Moore/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/warren-patterson/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Warren Patterson </a></em></p> <h2>Sugar market in surplus</h2> <p>Despite expectations for a global surplus in the sugar market in the 2024/25 season, sugar prices have held up relatively well. This has been largely due to concerns over</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1053940858/image_1053940858.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743865-global-sugar-surplus-depends-on-india", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 16:08:00"}, {"id": "4743403", "title": "The Fed Was Blindsided By Its $200 Billion Loss", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473080351/image_1473080351.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Financial Crisis\" data-id=\"1473080351\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473080351/image_1473080351.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473080351/image_1473080351.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473080351/image_1473080351.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473080351/image_1473080351.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473080351/image_1473080351.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473080351/image_1473080351.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473080351/image_1473080351.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473080351/image_1473080351.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">MCCAIG</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The Fed recently <a href=\"https://www.federalreserve.gov/aboutthefed/files/quarterly-report-20241122.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.federalreserve.gov/aboutthefed/files/quarterly-report-20241122.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">released</a> its financial statements for the third quarter. In this article, we're looking at the regulator\u2019s balance sheet and the fact that the Fed was not apparently able to forecast its own financial position.</p> <p>The regulator's interest</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473080351/image_1473080351.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743403-the-fed-was-blindsided-by-its-200-billion-loss", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 16:00:00"}, {"id": "4743859", "title": "Allspring Intermediate Tax/AMT-Free Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/680354062/image_680354062.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"money and ink pen on tax form\" data-id=\"680354062\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/680354062/image_680354062.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/680354062/image_680354062.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/680354062/image_680354062.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/680354062/image_680354062.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/680354062/image_680354062.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/680354062/image_680354062.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/680354062/image_680354062.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/680354062/image_680354062.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">liveslow/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Quarterly review </h2> <p>The fund underperformed its benchmark, the Bloomberg Municipal 1\u201315 Year Blend Index, for the three-month period that ended September 30, 2024. Security selection and credit were the largest drivers of underperformance. Yield curve and sector positioning were additive.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/680354062/image_680354062.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743859-allspring-intermediate-taxamt-free-fund-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 15:55:00"}, {"id": "4743835", "title": "Match: There May Be Hope With A Rebound In Tinder Payers And A New Capital Returns Plan (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358108003/image_1358108003.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Man uses a smartphone to flip through women\"s profiles and presses a heart button with his finger.' data-id=\"1358108003\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358108003/image_1358108003.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358108003/image_1358108003.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358108003/image_1358108003.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358108003/image_1358108003.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358108003/image_1358108003.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358108003/image_1358108003.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358108003/image_1358108003.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358108003/image_1358108003.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Lacheev</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Amid the voracious rally in the stock market that has lifted almost every industry to new heights, there has been a major holdout in the internet sector: Match (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MTCH\" title=\"Match Group, Inc.\">MTCH</a></span>), the largest portfolio of dating apps and the parent</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358108003/image_1358108003.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743835-match-there-may-be-hope-with-rebound-in-tinder-payers-and-a-new-capital-returns-plan-rating-upgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 15:45:26"}, {"id": "4743832", "title": "2 Ideal Buys From 50 'Safer' Dividends In 100 December Sustainables", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170026993/image_2170026993.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"two funny dogs in Christmas decoration, deer antlers. Festive border collie on green\" data-id=\"2170026993\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1135px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170026993/image_2170026993.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170026993/image_2170026993.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170026993/image_2170026993.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170026993/image_2170026993.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170026993/image_2170026993.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170026993/image_2170026993.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170026993/image_2170026993.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170026993/i